Plot: Today is Daisy's (Diego's Sister) La Fiesta de Quinceniera (15th Birthday). As Dora and Boots practice the Mambo dance, they receive a call from Daisy saying that she needs her Crown and Shoes for the party. The party cannot start without the celebrant's crown and shoes, so Dora and Boots had to hurry to give Daisy her special birthday present. Dora and Boots takes the fastest way to the party by going through the Barn, through the Rain Forest and to Daisy's party.
